This paper deals with information theory and network coding, which are typically covered in the cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) sub-categories. The paper also involves caching and delivery schemes, which are related to data structures (cs.DS) and systems and control (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses optimization and performance analysis, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG).
